{"tid":1134750,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"杜汶澤又道歉","createTime":"2019-05-02T01:19:29.000Z","updateTime":"2019-05-03T03:20:30.000Z","uid":129741,"like":25,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":22,"replies":[{"pid":"767d7b4c99c23dadff98cf1654968768706f89c1","tid":1134750,"uid":129741,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-02T01:19:30.000Z","msg":"「我自細都覺得呢個世界好唔公平，所以我自細有個夢想就係成為英雄，可以伸張正義、為民請命。後尾我發覺原來我把口幾叻，尤其是屌人嗰陣，即係俗稱『幾屌得』。後來我覺得原來屌人都可以伸張正義，咁屌屌下就嘗試到啲甜頭，有咗嗰種成就感，『屌中咗都幾過癮喎』。於是乎培養咗我好鍾意屌人嘅習慣，正所謂『係又屌唔係又屌、識又屌唔識又屌』，我意思係把口啫。咁屌下屌下就慣咗。有時會屌啱人，有時會屌錯人。<br />\n <br />\n最近就屌錯咗人啦。所以我今日鄭重向程美段小姐道歉。關於我話程美段小姐同記者講，話係『博見報』，我就呢一句說話係講對唔住。而我公司應承咗你一個禮拜就有錢俾你，結果係三個月之後先俾到你，我喺度同你講對唔住。我叫人哋小心你、儘量就唔好用你，係我唔啱，對唔住。我對你所有嘅指控，我都覺得我係錯嘅，對唔住。<br />\n <br />\n唔單只係程美段小姐，我對一生人入面所有我屌過嘅人，無論我屌啱你、屌錯你，都同你哋講對唔住。除咗中國共產黨。所有嘅人我都喺度同你哋道歉。<br />\n <br />\n舉頭三尺有神明，我今日喺關二哥面前發誓，我杜汶澤，以後唔再屌人。人哋有金盆洗手，我今日金盆洗撚，以後唔屌人。」<br />\n <br />\n── 喱騷CEO 杜汶澤（1/5/2019)<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"297242b865636a630df98bf869196fddec222655","tid":1134750,"uid":8717,"like":5,"dislike":5,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-02T01:20:49.000Z","msg":"妓女尚可相信"},{"pid":"136a284a4c7b979d676d6f08027280635e656d16","tid":1134750,"uid":198583,"like":3,"dislike":3,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-02T01:23:29.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">杜生雞蟲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span>"},{"pid":"f7bb568da35e44df14ee464d3aa5f8fc9ed7705b","tid":1134750,"uid":92603,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-02T01:24:02.000Z","msg":"陽萎？"},{"pid":"707787ab0780f2ece3ed905a14514134eada41a9","tid":1134750,"uid":5959,"like":13,"dislike":4,"score":9,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-02T01:24:45.000Z","msg":"道歉咪算，<br />\n係都要打篇我的志願嚟柒上柒"},{"pid":"34070690f0f88a273f11b7dc206fc081c5f885d5","tid":1134750,"uid":147047,"like":5,"dislike":13,"score":-8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-02T01:24:53.000Z","msg":"真男人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8f0886249c9074b2d0997a19ef5b030e8280e603","tid":1134750,"uid":85116,"like":16,"dislike":1,"score":15,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-02T01:25:11.000Z","msg":"其實佢知唔知鄭重依個詞點解"},{"pid":"36df74c3d625789b7e4e059a81c55d122c3b8a32","tid":1134750,"uid":59333,"like":0,"dislike":9,"score":-9,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-02T01:25:48.000Z","msg":"杜汶澤要做死狗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n都算係咁 仲以為會企硬<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"32de405e8c93686458fa2aa4fb99e48b8ec5ca3d","tid":1134750,"uid":76793,"like":6,"dislike":1,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-02T01:25:57.000Z","msg":"7撚到喊"},{"pid":"d24b9dd8ca682d9f3102694e2802711a5ab6b9bb","tid":1134750,"uid":43061,"like":6,"dislike":9,"score":-3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-02T01:26:48.000Z","msg":"杜狗都死狗道歉<br />\n佢班FANS仲屈9人五毛<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0ae32c1ce45f853c7b806320a60612cf533ee7fe","tid":1134750,"uid":178320,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-02T06:32:36.000Z","msg":"杜狗唔屌人既話， 等同冇牙狗一樣，仲有咩娛樂性<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5a38ed7f94e48bfc362d822790dab5ed1334bcfe","tid":1134750,"uid":49391,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-02T07:30:01.000Z","msg":"屌人之前,有無搞清事實呢?有無去求真呢?"},{"pid":"38fe0162de23a29f3394c34827c17fabd2f1fe6b","tid":1134750,"uid":171273,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-02T07:32:37.000Z","msg":"杜怯"},{"pid":"f743b81dbf05c4370b2fe6953fbd57c4c9a9ffa6","tid":1134750,"uid":21716,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"quote":{"pid":"297242b865636a630df98bf869196fddec222655","tid":1134750,"uid":8717,"like":5,"dislike":5,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-02T01:20:49.000Z","msg":"妓女尚可